@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@ownerUsername = li_ming
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@repeatableAdminTaskProjectName = create_task_admin_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatableOwnerTaskProjectName = create_task_owner_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatablePersonalTaskProjectName = create_task_personal_case_{{$timestamp}}
@candidateMemberUserId = 3
@enabledNonMemberUserId = 2
@completedProjectId = 3
@completedProjectNodeId = 3
@activeProjectWithCompletedNodeId = 1
@completedNodeIdInActiveProject = 1
@missingProjectId = 999999
@missingNodeId = 999999
@invalidProjectId = 0
@invalidNodeId = 0
@invalidResponsibleUserId = 0
@invalidPriority = 9

### 提示：正常路径会先创建临时项目、临时阶段节点，再创建子任务，因此可以重复回放。
### 提示：当前种子数据中，project 3（财务报表平台）为已完成项目；project 1（官网重构）下 node 1（需求分析）为已完成节点。
### 提示：enabledNonMemberUserId=2（li_ming）对管理员创建的临时项目默认不是成员，可用于验证 40907。
### 当前为 13.3 创建子任务 的联调用例；接口主链路已实现后再补到这里，按顺序回放即可。

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：管理员创建临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableAdminTaskProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证管理员创建子任务接口。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-30"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员创建临时阶段节点
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "开发实现",
  "description": "用于验证管理员在节点下创建子任务。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-05",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-15"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableAdminCreateTaskNodeId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员为临时项目添加成员 wang_jie
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": {{candidateMemberUserId}}
}

### 正常路径：管理员为成员 wang_jie 创建子任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskNodeId}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "接口联调",
  "description": "用于验证显式指定负责人创建子任务。",
  "responsible_user_id": {{candidateMemberUserId}},
  "priority": 3,
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-06",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-10"
}

### 正常路径：管理员不传 responsible_user_id 和 priority，默认由项目负责人负责且 priority=2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskNodeId}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "日志排查",
  "description": "用于验证默认负责人和默认优先级。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-11",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-14"
}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录创建子任务，预期 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskNodeId}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "未登录子任务",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-06",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-10"
}

