### 异常路径：项目已完成，不允许创建子任务，预期 409（40904）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{completedProjectId}}/nodes/{{completedProjectNodeId}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "已完成项目子任务",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-01-10",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-01-12"
}

### 异常路径：阶段节点已完成，不允许创建子任务，预期 409（40905）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{activeProjectWithCompletedNodeId}}/nodes/{{completedNodeIdInActiveProject}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "已完成节点子任务",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-03-02",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-03-04"
}

### 异常路径：子任务负责人不是当前项目成员，预期 409（40907）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskNodeId}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "非法负责人子任务",
  "responsible_user_id": {{enabledNonMemberUserId}},
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-06",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-10"
}

### 异常路径：planned_start_date 晚于 planned_end_date，预期 409（40909）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskNodeId}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "非法日期顺序子任务",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-12",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-10"
}

### 异常路径：子任务时间区间超出所属节点范围，预期 409（40909）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminCreateTaskNodeId}}/subtasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "越界日期子任务",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-04",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-10"
}

